title: Denmark Lending Rate
description: Denmark Lending Rate was at 1.40 percent on Thursday November 10. Lending Rate in Denmark averaged 2.62 percent from 1992 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 15 percent in November of 1992 and a record low of -0.45 percent in September of 2021. This page provides - Denmark Lending Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Danmarks Nationalbank
